title: #75 Tyler McCann Rendezvous City Beef Roundup
subtitle: #75 Tyler McCann Rendezvous City Beef Roundup
summary:
This week CK come back from her very bust day job at Vence to talk with a guest that has a very unique event coming up in Wyoming very soon. We are talking about the Rendezvous City Beef Roundup to be held in Riverton Wyoming on September 10th 2022.

Join us as we visit with the event's founder Tyler McCann as he gives us all the details.
